{"tid":1979390,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"熟悉美國人士: 香港成為中美角力場, 美國可能落實對香港抗爭者提供政治庇護。","createTime":"2020-04-19T11:29:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T14:28:21.000Z","uid":134071,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"17d05af4ccaaa76c723a9d35136e31c423709b63","tid":1979390,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T11:29:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200419/NCURSIZEYZUFVG6JRSB2G4MHTA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200419%2FNCURSIZEYZUFVG6JRSB2G4MHTA%2F&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWvS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=19bf1cb2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200419%2FNCURSIZEYZUFVG6JRSB2G4MHTA%2F&h=02f42486\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200419/NCURSIZEYZUFVG6JRSB2G4MHTA/</a><br />\n<br />\n【4.18大圍捕】美司法部長指「再證明中共不可信」 勢影響對港引渡及政治庇護政策<br />\n39分鐘<br />\n....<br />\n有熟悉美國政情局勢人士認為，中方銳意取代美國模式民主，香港無可避免成為戰場，但認為中方舉動勢影響美國對港的海關以至引渡政策，甚至有可能落實對港抗爭者提供政治庇護。<br />\n....<br />\n國際社會對大搜捕高度關注，美國國務卿蓬佩奧、眾議院議長佩洛西都先後發聲，有熟悉美國政情局勢人士分析，最值得留意的是美國司法部長巴爾（William Barr）的聲明，相信是歷來首次有美國司法部長就香港政治檢控問題發聲明，該聲明嚴詞指出，今次針對民主派的大圍捕行動是對香港法治和港人自由的最新攻擊，反映中共的價值觀與西方自由民主制度中享有的價值觀截然相反，與中方在美國的惡意影響和工業間諜活動相提並論，更直言：「再一次證明中共是不可信」。該人士認為美方會對香港執法機構視為中國政府一部份，有機會觸動美方改變對港的海關出入口管制、引渡政策，甚至可能對流亡美國的香港抗爭者給予政治庇護。<br />\n<br />\n該人士續指，美方相信中方仍然對受制裁有所擔憂，只是親北京陣營要將針對性行動與勾結外國勢掛鈎，合理化其行動，又形容中方銳意取代由美國領頭的民主模式，香港就自然成為兩方的角力場。"},{"pid":"16184d0e97f981bb30a4719a5451a6e99c19ebea","tid":1979390,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T11:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99cec4d3a062e221cd264deaa2ea629e5835ba3d","tid":1979390,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T11:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867010c7a29aa8e99ee01d272e219298ede61502","tid":1979390,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T11:46:34.000Z","msg":"O'er the land of the free and the home of the brave <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.britannica.com/33/4833-050-0FE70191/Flag-United-States-of-America.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.britannica.com%2F33%2F4833-050-0FE70191%2FFlag-United-States-of-America.jpg&h=e6fccc23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9503cac3600eee4bd0da0df1307204b69d619462","tid":1979390,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"867010c7a29aa8e99ee01d272e219298ede61502","tid":1979390,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T11:46:34.000Z","msg":"O'er the land of the free and the home of the brave <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.britannica.com/33/4833-050-0FE70191/Flag-United-States-of-America.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.britannica.com%2F33%2F4833-050-0FE70191%2FFlag-United-States-of-America.jpg&h=e6fccc23&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T11:47:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf208298ef79ad1e6c6149b0857bbf2b4323e22","tid":1979390,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T11:59:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TheJusticeDept/status/1251699842059046914\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheJusticeDept%2Fstatus%2F1251699842059046914&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWvS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfW